    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7274.0,
      "end_time": 13276.0,
      "text": "But in the meantime, this is a great opportunity to explain why our nation's prison system is a failure on every level."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13313.0,
      "end_time": 15616.0,
      "text": "Ha! So you know   a lot about prison?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15616.0,
      "end_time": 18018.0,
      "text": "I bet you watch a lot   of PBS documentaries, huh?"
