    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 27327.0,
      "end_time": 28328.0,
      "text": "Whoa!"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 28328.0,
      "end_time": 30130.0,
      "text": "Do you have magic TV powers like Adam?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 30130.0,
      "end_time": 33567.0,
      "text": "Nope, but I got a lot of favors."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 34568.0,
      "end_time": 36803.0,
      "text": "Early lunch today."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 36803.0,
      "end_time": 38739.0,
      "text": "Early lunch today,   everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 38739.0,
      "end_time": 40874.0,
      "text": "America's prison system    is a total mess."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 40874.0,
      "end_time": 43477.0,
      "text": "Whatever purpose you think  it serves, it ain't doing it."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 43477.0,
      "end_time": 45712.0,
      "text": "Well, the point of prison    is to reduce crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 45712.0,
      "end_time": 47781.0,
      "text": "It's definitely not   doing that."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 47781.0,
      "end_time": 50182.0,
      "text": "There are  2.2 million people incarcerated in the U.S.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 50184.0,
      "end_time": 52486.0,
      "text": "ten times more   than 50 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 52486.0,
      "end_time": 55689.0,
      "text": "Two million is more than the population of some states."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 55689.0,
      "end_time": 58425.0,
      "text": "Welcome to Mass-Incarceration-   Achusetts."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 58425.0,
      "end_time": 60661.0,
      "text": "Our primary export-- shivs."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 60661.0,
      "end_time": 63497.0,
      "text": "Our secondary export-- cod!"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 63497.0,
      "end_time": 66567.0,
      "text": "Hey! That's cod-traband."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 66567.0,
      "end_time": 68869.0,
      "text": "(laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 68869.0,
      "end_time": 71537.0,
      "text": "But despite  this massive increase in the prison population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 71605.0,
      "end_time": 73841.0,
      "text": "a study conducted    by the NYU School of Law"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 73841.0,
      "end_time": 77842.0,
      "text": "found that the effect    on the crime rate has been essentially zero."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 77911.0,
      "end_time": 80681.0,
      "text": "Zero? Then why do we lock    so many people up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 80681.0,
      "end_time": 82316.0,
      "text": "Well, I can't speak    for all prisons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 82316.0,
      "end_time": 84251.0,
      "text": "but this one is here to make money."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 84251.0,
      "end_time": 85853.0,
      "text": "Make money?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 85853.0,
      "end_time": 87955.0,
      "text": "You mean someone is profiting from all this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 87955.0,
      "end_time": 91625.0,
      "text": "Yep, these guys are."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 91625.0,
      "end_time": 94194.0,
      "text": "It all started in the \"tough on crime\" '80s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 94194.0,
      "end_time": 97696.0,
      "text": "when the war on drugs meant state and federal prisons were bursting at the seams."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 97764.0,
      "end_time": 99800.0,
      "text": "So many prisoners? What do we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 99800.0,
      "end_time": 101835.0,
      "text": "Let corporate America    handle your prisons."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 101835.0,
      "end_time": 103136.0,
      "text": "We'll take care  of everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 103136.0,
      "end_time": 105638.0,
      "text": "Save you a few bucks and skim a little    off the top."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 105672.0,
      "end_time": 107307.0,
      "text": "Businesses running prisons?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 107307.0,
      "end_time": 108942.0,
      "text": "That sounds a little fishy."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 108942.0,
      "end_time": 111512.0,
      "text": "(laughing) Just kidding!"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 111512.0,
      "end_time": 114615.0,
      "text": "I mean, hey, if it saves money, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 114615.0,
      "end_time": 119115.0,
      "text": "And so the Corrections Corporation of America, or CCA, was born."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 119119.0,
      "end_time": 124655.0,
      "text": "Okay, hold on.   You can't just sell prisons like they're cars or real estate  or hamburgers."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 124758.0,
      "end_time": 127261.0,
      "text": "Hmph! Then why don't you    tell that to Tom Beasleyã€‚"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 127261.0,
      "end_time": 134201.0,
      "text": "the co-founder of CCA    who once said...\"YOU JUST SELL PRISONS LIKE YOU WERE SELLING CARS, OR REAL ESTATE, OR  HAMBURGERS.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 134201.0,
      "end_time": 135502.0,
      "text": "CCA, can I take your order?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 135502.0,
      "end_time": 139439.0,
      "text": "I'll have a number seven   with extra solitary cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 139439.0,
      "end_time": 141775.0,
      "text": "electric fence,   and small onion rings."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 141775.0,
      "end_time": 142275.0,
      "text": "Like to supermax that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 142275.0,
      "end_time": 143744.0,
      "text": "Yeah, I'll supermax it."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 143744.0,
      "end_time": 145612.0,
      "text": "And they rake in    a ton of scratch."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 145612.0,
      "end_time": 149283.0,
      "text": "Last year, CCA    took in $1.7 billion."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 149283.0,
      "end_time": 151618.0,
      "text": "Business is so good it's criminal."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 151618.0,
      "end_time": 153554.0,
      "text": "(laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 153554.0,
      "end_time": 154788.0,
      "text": "Well, you know, maybe it's okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 154788.0,
      "end_time": 156657.0,
      "text": "Because they're saving the taxpayer money."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 156657.0,
      "end_time": 159092.0,
      "text": "Sorry! The sales pitch   was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 159092.0,
      "end_time": 164161.0,
      "text": "The data shows that private prisons cost the taxpayers   just as much as regular prisons."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 164198.0,
      "end_time": 168867.0,
      "text": "And today, nearly one-fifth  of federal prisoners are held    in a for-profit facility."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 168936.0,
      "end_time": 170103.0,
      "text": "Okay, no--"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 170103.0,
      "end_time": 173941.0,
      "text": "Ah, graffiti!  That's an infraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 173941.0,
      "end_time": 176510.0,
      "text": "A beautiful one. Are you Banksy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 176510.0,
      "end_time": 179847.0,
      "text": "Oh, my gosh, I already got an infraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 179847.0,
      "end_time": 181315.0,
      "text": "They must give out a lot of these."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 181315.0,
      "end_time": 184751.0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, that's not a coincidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 184751.0,
      "end_time": 189820.0,
      "text": "One study showed  that private prisons dole out twice as many   infractions as government prisons."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 189790.0,
      "end_time": 192192.0,
      "text": "Not having enough infractions."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 192192.0,
      "end_time": 194428.0,
      "text": "That's an infraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 194428.0,
      "end_time": 196230.0,
      "text": "These penalties   can lengthen your sentence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 196230.0,
      "end_time": 198065.0,
      "text": "which earns the company even more cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 198065.0,
      "end_time": 199499.0,
      "text": "Oh, so the more people   that are in prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 199499.0,
      "end_time": 200968.0,
      "text": "the more money   they make."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 200968.0,
      "end_time": 202636.0,
      "text": "Ooh, that's dirty!"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 202636.0,
      "end_time": 206838.0,
      "text": "Yep, that's why private prisons sneak occupancy clauses into their contracts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 206840.0,
      "end_time": 210010.0,
      "text": "which actually require states to keep prisons full."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 210010.0,
      "end_time": 214912.0,
      "text": "Last year, a private prison   in Arizona didn't make    their 97% capacity quota,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 214948.0,
      "end_time": 218217.0,
      "text": "so the state government had to pay them a $3 million fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 218252.0,
      "end_time": 223454.0,
      "text": "Fines like that incentivize cash-strapped states to keep people in prison as long as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 223490.0,
      "end_time": 227459.0,
      "text": "Your parole forms    are in order and you've been    a model prisoner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 227461.0,
      "end_time": 227961.0,
      "text": "so we're going to--"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 227961.0,
      "end_time": 229296.0,
      "text": "(clears throat)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 229296.0,
      "end_time": 231064.0,
      "text": "Lock you back up."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 231064.0,
      "end_time": 234234.0,
      "text": "We really can't afford   to pay another fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 234234.0,
      "end_time": 236737.0,
      "text": "That's reprehensible."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 236737.0,
      "end_time": 238972.0,
      "text": "Look, not all prisons  are private prisons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 238972.0,
      "end_time": 240407.0,
      "text": "but this one is. So no,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 240407.0,
      "end_time": 242209.0,
      "text": "it's purpose  isn't to stop crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 242209.0,
      "end_time": 244244.0,
      "text": "It's the dollar-dollar bills, y'all!"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 244244.0,
      "end_time": 246180.0,
      "text": "Whoo!"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 246180.0,
      "end_time": 249381.0,
      "text": "I can't believe all this has been happening and I didn't even know."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 249449.0,
      "end_time": 252152.0,
      "text": "I mean, I never thought  about prison, like, at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 252152.0,
      "end_time": 255487.0,
      "text": "Hey, pulling back the curtain on our disturbing   business practices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 255589.0,
